# Architecture Diagrams

This directory contains Mermaid diagram sources (.mmd) and generated images (.svg).

## Usage

- Place .mmd files here for architecture diagrams
- Run diagram-to-image agent to convert to SVG
- Reference in markdown: `![Diagram](./diagrams/name.svg)`

## Naming Convention

- system-overview.mmd - System component layout
- data-flow.mmd - Request/response flows
- data-model.mmd - ER diagram of entities
- {feature}-flow.mmd - Feature-specific flows
